The order of 7 parameters of the USER's function
COMPONENT of COEFFICIENT ahead the INITIAL STRESSES
at time TEMPS, at point X,Y,Z, 
for the PLSVO of type number NO_TYPE_OBJECT
(1:POINT, 2:LINE, 3:SURFACE, 4:VOLUME, 5:OBJECT )
the directory number NO_OBJECT
NO_COMP number of the INITIAL STRESSES
must be

INIT_STRES( TEMPS, X, Y, Z, NO_TYPE_OBJET, NO_OBJET, NO_COMP ) 

and be programmed with respect to LU grammar
(cf documentation and examples of the debut menu)

All these parameters will be initialized during its call.
These parameters can be used or not, but have to be present
in the definition of INIT_STRES.
 
EXAMPLE:
deffunc init_stress( t, x, y, z, no_type_objet, materiau, nc );
if  materiau=nuobjt( 'volume' , 'acier' )
then 
  if nc<4
  then  init_stress=1e6; 
  else  init_stress=0;
  endif ;
else
  if  materiau=nuobjt( 'volume' , 'cuivre' )
  then 
    if nc<4
    then init_stress= 2e5 ;
    else init_stress= 0;
    endif;  
  endif;   
endif;
endfunc; 

Remark: the LU function nuobjt( p1, p2 ) gives the
number of the PLSVO of type p1 with the name p2.
